headline: Review & Preview: We’re Back!
summary: Outages related to Amazon Web Services hit a number of major websites and services, including Barron’s, but we were back in action as the afternoon rolled on.  The stock market didn’t lose a beat.  The Nasdaq Composite rallied 1.4%.

headline: Healthy Paws Partners with Airvet to Make Veterinary Care More Accessible Via Telehealth
summary: Healthy Paws, a Chubb company and a leading provider of accident and illness pet insurance coverage for dogs and cats, today announced a partnership with Airvet, the nation's leading veterinary telehealth platform, to ensure that pet families across the country have instant access to world-class veterinarians to get care when they need it most.
